            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp><app><note>Text of Bitto 2001</note></app></listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#VB">
                <p> To the Shades of the Underworld. Cartilia Irene lived 38 years. Claudius Theseus to (his) most pure wife</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="#VB">
                <p> Alle ombre dell'aldilà. Cartilia Irene visse 38 anni. Claudio Teseo per la (sua) purissima moglie</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" resp="#JP">
                <p>Three other texts from the same necropolis were also set up by Claudius Thesis, two in Greek (<ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic3529">ISic3529</ref>, <ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic3530">ISic3530</ref>) and a second in Latin (<ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic0787">ISic0787</ref>).</p>
            </div>
